{"title_page": "List of Bunk'd episodes", "text_new": "{{short description|Wikipedia list article}}\n{{italic title|string=Bunk'd}}\n''[[Bunk'd]]'' is an American [[comedy]] television series created by [[Pamela Eells O'Connell]] that premiered on [[Disney Channel]] on July 31, 2015. The series is a spinoff of ''[[Jessie (2011 TV series)|Jessie]]'' and includes returning stars [[Peyton List (actress, born 1998)|Peyton List]], [[Karan Brar]], and [[Skai Jackson]]. Starring alongside them is Miranda May.\n\n== Series overview ==\n<!-- full linking is used in the following template because it is transcluded to the main series article -->\n\n<onlyinclude>{{Series overview\n\n| color1    = #F5DEB3\n| link1     = <includeonly>List of Bunk'd episodes</includeonly>#Season 1 (2015\u201316)\n| episodes1 = 21\n| start1    = {{Start date|2015|7|31}}\n| end1      = {{End date|2016|5|20}}\n\n| color2    = #355E3B\n| link2     = <includeonly>List of Bunk'd episodes</includeonly>#Season 2 (2016\u201317)\n| episodes2 = 21\n| start2    = {{Start date|2016|8|23}}\n| end2      = {{End date|2017|5|24}}\n\n| color3    = #1034A6\n| link3     = <includeonly>List of Bunk'd episodes</includeonly>#Season 3 (2018)\n| episodes3 = 16\n| start3    = {{Start date|2018|6|18}}\n| end3      = {{End date|2018|9|21}}\n\n| color4    = #000000\n| link4     = <includeonly>List of Bunk'd episodes</includeonly>#Season 4 (2019\u201320)\n| episodes4 = 25\n| start4    = {{Start date|2019|6|20}}\n| end4      = [[TBA]]\n\n}}</onlyinclude>\n\n== Episodes ==\n\n=== Season 1 (2015\u201316) ===\n{{Episode table\n| background      = #F5DEB3\n| overall         = \n| season          = \n| title           = \n| titleR          = <ref name=\"The Futon Critic\" /><ref name=\"Zap2it Season 1\" />\n| director        = \n| writer          = \n| airdate         = \n| airdateR        = <ref name=\"The Futon Critic\" /><ref name=\"Zap2it Season 1\" />\n| prodcode        = \n| prodcodeR       = <ref name=\"Copyright Office\" /><